-- New Zealand Will Proceed With Emissions Trading Plan in July on Schedule
-- Tracy Withers
-- 2010-04-28T01:50:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-28/new-zealand-will-proceed-with-emissions-trading-plan-in-july-on-schedule.html

          
          
             New Zealand will proceed with an
emissions trading plan on July 1 as previously announced,
Climate Change Minister Nick Smith said in an e-mailed
statement. There would be real instability and uncertainty in
deferring the introduction of the plan at this stage, he said.  
          
          


  


        